Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:36.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey, {\alpha&HFF&}monkey, monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:36.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey, monkey, {\alpha&HFF&}monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monkey, monkey, monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.90,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Monkey, monkey, monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wow! Che figata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È proprio fighissimo!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.15,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma come?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:50.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quaranta metri all'obiettivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trenta metri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Venti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:56.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dieci!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:00.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Barco-Hunter Joint:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:02.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Completato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bene!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Si comincia a soffiare!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sissignore!\N– Sissignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non dirmi che...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ha intenzione di portare su la \Nnave riempiendola d'aria da solo?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:22.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma è un metodo assurdo...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aria?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lo scafo si sta alzando!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ora! Tiratela su!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sissignore!\N– Sissignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non sbagliate il tempismo \Ncon la fornitura d'aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sissignore!\N– Sissignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,L'equipaggio che si è immerso...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Che è successo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:16.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Che vi è successo,\N miei piccoli scagnozzi?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'è qualcuno dentro alla nave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dannato, come osi attaccare\N i miei piccoli scagnozzi!?{Tony}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chi diamine ti credi di essere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:40.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Guarda che non ti stiamo mica\N fotografando o cose del genere...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Si era messo in posa per una foto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boss! Salvaci!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arrivo subito!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Continuate a tirare su la nave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sissignore!\N– Sissignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pugno Scimmia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, sta salendo, eh?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Visto? Stiamo bene \Nanche se togliamo i barili.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non pensavo potessero \Nmandarci così tanta aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:33.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Però, chi diavolo sta\N tirando su questa nave?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:37.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Potrebbe essere successo \Nqualcosa a Nami e Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non rispondono da un pezzo\N anche se le chiamo!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chi diavolo è...{Tony}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}che si sta scatenando nel mio territorio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:45.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah... è una scimmia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sono davvero così {\i1}scimmialto{\i0}?{Presumo usi lo stesso termine di prima, poi confermami o meno Nikki -Cora}{yes, è lo stesso -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sì, assomiglia un bel po' a una scimmia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma che razza di conversazione è?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quale?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comunque, tu chi saresti?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:03.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, mi fai arrossire così~{per rimanere coerenti a 12:09 -Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:06.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lo pensi davvero? \NCerto che hai buon gusto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ci vuoi dire chi sei o no?!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ehi, sotto la nave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:20.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sì, c'è qualcosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capisco! Quindi siete dell'East Blue!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:32.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esatto! Però, tu somigli proprio \Nun sacco a una scimmia!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Così mi lusinghi troppo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:53.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ma che–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:59.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E questo che cos'è?! Cos'è questo!?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=71}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=74}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
